ap2it.com/2015/05/19/sunday-final-ratings-the-simpsons-billboard-music-awards-adjusted-up/405808/|title=Sunday Final Ratings: 'The Simpsons' & 'Billboard Music Awards' Adjusted Up|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|work=TV by the Numbers|date=May 19, 2015|accessdate=May 19, 2015}}</ref>\n| season2           = 2014\u201315\n| rank2             = 113<ref name=\"deadline2015Ratings\">{{cite magazine|url=https://deadline.com/2015/05/2014\u201315-full-tv-season-ratings-shows-rankings\u20131201431167/|title=Full 2014\u20132015 TV Season Series Rankings|date=August 23, 2014|magazine=Deadline}}</ref>\n| viewers2          = 4.87<ref name=\"deadline2015Ratings\" />\n\n| link3             = Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 3)\n| episodes3         = 23\n| timeslot3         = Sunday 8:30 pm {{small|(1\u201310)}}<br />Tuesday 9:00 pm {{small|(11\u201323)}}\n| start3            = {{Start date|2015|9|27}}\n| startrating3      = 3.14<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/09/29/sunday-final-ratings-bobs-burgers-adjusted-down-60-minutes-adjusted-up-sunday-night-football/473898/|title=Sunday Final Ratings: 'Bob's Burgers' Adjusted Down, '60 Minutes' Adjusted Up + 'Sunday Night Football'|last=Dixon|first=Dani|date=September 29, 2015|work=TVbytheNumbers|accessdate=September 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| end3              = {{End date|2016|4|19}}\n| endrating3        = 2.02<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/04/20/tuesday-final-ratings-april\u201319-2016/|title=Tuesday Final Ratings: 'NCIS' and 'The Flash' adjust up, 'Containment' adjusts down|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=April 20, 2016|accessdate=April 20, 2016|publisher=TV by the Numbers}}{{Dead link|date=November 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n| season3           = 2015\u201316\n| rank3             = 118<ref name=\"entertainment2016b99\" />\n| viewers3          = 3.98<ref name=\"entertainment2016b99\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2016/05/tv-season-2015-2016-series-rankings-shows-full-list\u20131201763189/|title=Full 2015\u201316 TV Season Series Rankings|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 26, 2015|accessdate=May 26, 2015}}</ref>\n\n| link4             = Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 4)\n| episodes4         = 22\n| timeslot4         = Tuesday 8:00 pm {{small|(1\u201310, 13\u201322)}}<br/>Sunday 8:30 pm {{small|(11\u201312)}}\n| start4            = {{Start date|2016|9|20}}\n| startrating4      = 2.39<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/09/21/tuesday-final-ratings-sept-20-2016/|title=Tuesday final ratings: 'NCIS,' 'Brooklyn Nine-Nine' adjust up, 'This Is Us' & 'Bull' steady|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=September 21, 2016|accessdate=September 21, 2016|publisher=TV by the Numbers}}</ref>\n| end4              = {{End date|2017|5|23}}\n| endrating4        = 1.50<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-may-23-2017/|title='Dancing With the Stars finale adjusts up, 'iZombie' adjusts down: Tuesday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=TV by the Numbers|date=May 24, 2017|accessdate=May 24, 2017}}</ref>\n| season4           = 2016\u201317\n| rank4             = 137<ref name=\"entertainment2017\" />\n| viewers4          = 2.87<ref name=\"entertainment2017\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/05/2016-2017-tv-season-ratings-series-rankings-list\u20131202102340/|title=Final 2016\u201317 TV Rankings: 'Sunday Night Football' Winning Streak Continues|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 26, 2017|accessdate=May 26, 2017}}</ref>\n\n| link5             = Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 5)\n| episodes5         = 22\n| timeslot5         = Tuesday 9:30 pm {{small|(1\u201311)}}<br />Sunday 8:30 pm {{small|(12\u201322)}}\n| start5            = {{Start date|2017|9|26}}\n| startrating5      = 2.00<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-sept-26-2017/|title='Bull,' 'Voice,' 'This Is Us' adjust up, 'L&O True Crime' and 'Brooklyn Nine-Nine' down: Tuesday final ra